Author: geoffreymoya
Title: [ANN][ICO]SATT -🔥THE NEW ERA OF ADVERTISING🔥
Body: Campaign creation The advertiser is the one who pays the money (SaTT tokens in this case) to get his advertisement shown. In order to get the most from SaTT advertising campaign system dApp, here is how it works from the Advertiser’s side.  1- First, access your Wallet through   https://satt.atayen.us   2- Then click on “Advertiser” in “Campaigns” tab    3- Then click on “Create a new campaign”  4- This Popup will be displayed for you, now fill Campaign’s General info and description    Infos :  A – Insert the title of the campaign that will be displayed to the public B – Insert tags are made to facilitate the search of the campaigns C – Insert the amount of tokens you’re willing to pay per CPM D – Insert maximum total payment you’re willing to pay for this campaign E – Insert maximum duration to underline the deadline of the campaign F – Insert the image that will appear to public as a cover photo of your campaign G – Insert description.Try to make this part attractive to publishers, it’s a summary  5- Insert the campaign’s KIT in the second pop up      Number 1 and 2 are for the Kit whether a link or file to help the publisher define and build your campaign. 3 is for the Kit you have entered.  6- Click on “Launch the campaign” at the bottom of this popup.  7- Then click on “validate” and enter your Wallet’s security password.    Now your campaign is being registered on the Blockchain don’t get fed up by waiting a couple of minutes at maximum.  PS: You need GAS to execute this process.  7- Do not close the pop up until process is completed  Finally your campaign is now public and visible to all publishers.  The selection of candidates Now that your campaign is public, the list of candidates that have applied will be shown to you :  1- Click on advertiser  2- Click on the particular campaign  3- Then click on “Candidates” button in the right menu as follows :    You can select or reject one candidate or more.  The selection of videos This is the final part in order to complete the final selection and get your campaign started you should  1- Click on advertiser  2- Open your campaign from your dashboard and click on “Videos” button in the right sided menu  3- Accept or reject the video    Now get your content published !

Author: S3cco
Title: [ANN][ICO]SATT -🔥THE NEW ERA OF ADVERTISING🔥
Body: Bitcoin Garden: Facebook iFrames App Developer Atayen Launches ‘When Moon’ SaTT ICO Game https://bitcoingarden.org/facebook-iframes-app-developer-atayen-launches-when-moon-satt-ico-game/  Atayen, creator of the ERC-20 SaTT token which facilitates advertising transactions with a smart contract, is pleased to announce the launch of their new ICO crypto game, “When Moon?”  Together with “When Lambo?”, “When Moon?” is one of the most popular phrases used in the crypto universe, to question when a crypto investment will yield extremely lucrative profits. Aptly combining these two elements, the objective of the game is to skyrocket your favorite tokens to the moon to win Lambos (Lamborghinis). Through various moves such as dumping your boosters or upgrading your rocket to propel it to go as high as possible, players play with the aim of reaching the moon and winning Lambos. Players who choose to publish their scores are then entered into a weekly classification where the highest scorer gets to win tokens from the token sponsor, no doubt an innovative and fun way for crypto enthusiasts to earn tokens. Each player can personalize the skin of his rocket with his favorite token. Currently a selection of 3 different token-skins are available – SaTT, Jetcoin and Ethereum....

In my opinion, the greatest success factor of a project is the support of an active community and taking into consideration its opinion, values that we have honoured since the beginning of ATAYEN, and that we apply to the SaTT project.  Therefore we updated the SaTT project as well as the Whitepaper in order to answer both the community’s comments and those of the experts in the sector. Indeed, we received a lot of feedback after the launch of our project. We were able to meet experts such as Crypto-Analysis, Chaineum, ICOBox, Cryptopotatoe, Miguel RT, TheRightICO, Cointelegraph, Amazix... who gave us precious advice.   Technical wallet update:   - Improvement of the website: www.satt-token.com  - Registration without Facebook, addition of Google Connect and registration and Login SaTT  - Added airdrop 25 SaTT for completion KYC  - Addition of 5% + 5% affiliate affiliation  - Improvement of the general ergonomics of the wallet  - Adding a transaction history  - Update of contact management  - Free ETH offer to initiate transactions  To test the new version of the Wallet, click HERE  Whitepaper update:   - Date of the end of the ICO changed to September 30th  - Hardcap changed to $ 49.5M  - Choice to burn undistributed tokens instead of re-allocating them to the reserve  - Establishment of a vesting plan for the partners and the team to block these tokens for a period of 1 year then a progressive release for 10 months to avoid a brutal dump on the market  - Adding renowned advisors  Download the updated Whitepaper, click HERE  Purchase guarantee  These last few weeks have been harsh on cryptocurrencies with significant drops that are slowing down investments. In order to guarantee your SaTT purchase at the best price, we set up a sure solution : if you buy today and the course of Ether or Bitcoin is higher during the last step of the ICO, we will pay you the difference in SaTT at the beginning of this step.  Extension of the Bounty  We have decided to extend our Bounty till the end of the ICO in September. If you want to check the new rules and the modifications, click HERE   We want to thank all participants, the experts who allow us to improve ourselves, and we assure you of the complete devotion of the team aiming towards SaTT’s success! We are available on Telegram as well as our Facebook page, feel free to get in touch with us!  Yours truly, Gauthier BROS, CEO of SaTT
